data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 1120 Hendon Loop, where elegance and comfort converge in perfect harmony. Nestled in the heart of Davenport, this stunning residence redefines modern living with its exceptional design and lavish amenities.    Key Features:   Seller is offering $5000, towards closing costs/pre-paid or rate buy down :-)     Elegance Meets Comfort: Step into a world of sophistication as you enter this meticulously designed property. The open-concept layout effortlessly blends luxurious details with comfortable living spaces, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Custom Touches throughout!     Gourmet Chef's Kitchen: The heart of this home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, and a sprawling center island. It's the perfect place to unleash your inner chef and entertain guests.     Master Retreat: The master suite is a sanctuary of tranquility, offering a spacious oasis to unwind in after a long day. The en-suite bathroom features a spa-like soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and dual vanities for added convenience.     Outdoor Paradise: Step outside to your own private paradise. The screened lanai is the ideal spot for al fresco dining and relaxation, overlooking a beautifully landscaped backyard with lush greenery and room for a pool if desired.     Community Amenities: Located in a sought-after community, you'll have access to amenities like a clubhouse, swimming pool, and fitness center. There's always something to do right at your doorstep.    Location Highlights:     Convenience: Enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and top-rated schools, making this property an ideal choice for families.     Disney Magic: Just a short drive away from Walt Disney World Resort, you can experience the magic of Disney whenever you please.     Golf Enthusiasts' Haven: Several world-class golf courses are in close proximity, catering to golfers of all skill levels.    Don't miss the opportunity to own this exquisite residence at 1120 Hendon Loop. It's more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Schedule your private showing today and make this piece of paradise your own!    The Roof, AC, Water Heater and Plumbing are ALL only 3 years old! This home is MOVE-IN READY! This property qualifies for USDA financing!!!
